What is AOT compilation in Angular ??
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CefpOrZF4Uw
Process of converting angular application code into javascript code during build phase before the application is deployed 
into client's browser.
In JIT angular code is compiled in the client's browser at run time.
Compiling the application during build phase 

Differences between JIT and AOT compilation in Angular ??

JIT is the type of the compilation that compiles your app in the browser at the runtime.

ng build
ng serve

AOT is the type of compilation which compiles your app at the runtime.
